You can reuse the #create(KubernetesList... items) method so logic will be the same in both scenarios:




        Suggested change











              @Override



              public KubernetesList create(KubernetesList list) {



                if (list.getItems().isEmpty()) {



                  list = get();



                }



                return new KubernetesListBuilder().withItems(createItemsInKubernetesList(list)).build();



              }



              @SuppressWarnings("squid:S3878")



              @Override



              public KubernetesList create(KubernetesList list) {



                return create(new KubernetesList[]{list});



              }

